		<p class="text-text mb-4">
			Now the refactoring begins. This plan runs with a fresh context — it reads the plan file and the current code (which now includes the tests from Plan 1). The goal: move all JSON file I/O into a dedicated storage module with a clean interface. The main file should never touch the filesystem directly.
